snippet.title: Stikbold Announcement Trailer | PS4, XB1 & PC
snippet.description:
Stikbold! is a groovy 70s-themed single and local multiplayer fantasy dodgeball game with quirky arenas and chaos-inducing random events.

Follow the story of world famous Stikbold atheletes Björn and Jerome, play solo, team up with a dodgeball buddy in co-op battles, or charge head first into a manic free-for-all battles with up to five others.

Stikbold! is coming soon to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC.

http://www.stikbold.com/
http://curve-digital.com/
